room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Mastermind Escape Games in Atlanta
room_address: 5825 Glenridge Dr Building 4 Suite #200, Atlanta, GA 30328
room_description: As your final test to become a part of a world-renowned crime syndicate, you have to rob the Atlanta bank. Your boss will distract the guards and cops for an hour. The task is not just to escape, but to steal as much cash as possible.
